'''尼帕病毒感染'''是由[[尼帕病毒|尼帕病毒]]引起的[[病毒性疾病|病毒性疾病]]。<ref name="WHO2020">{{Cite web|title=Nipah Virus (NiV) Infection|url=https://www.who.int/csr/disease/nipah/en/|accessdate=14 October 2020|work=World Health Organization (WHO)|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926040108/https://www.who.int/csr/disease/nipah/en/|archivedate=26 September 2020}}</ref>感染者可能无症状，也可能[[发热|发烧]]、咳嗽、头痛、[[呼吸困难|呼吸急促]]和神志不清，<ref name="CDC2014Sym">{{Cite web|title=Signs and Symptoms Nipah Virus (NiV)|url=https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/symptoms/index.html|accessdate=24 May 2018|work=CDC|language=en-us|archive-date=2019-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190615124230/https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/symptoms/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>一两天之内可能恶化为[[昏迷|昏迷]]。有50％至75％的被感染者死亡。并发症可能包括[[脑炎|脑部炎症]]和恢复后的[[癲癇發作|癫痫发作]]。 

尼帕病毒（NiV）是[[亨尼巴病毒属|亨尼巴病毒属]]的一种[[核糖核酸病毒|RNA病毒]]，<ref name="WHO2020">{{Cite web|title=Nipah Virus (NiV) Infection|url=https://www.who.int/csr/disease/nipah/en/|accessdate=14 October 2020|work=World Health Organization (WHO)|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926040108/https://www.who.int/csr/disease/nipah/en/|archivedate=26 September 2020}}</ref>通常在特定种类的[[狐蝠科|果蝠]]之间传播。尼帕病毒既可以在人与人之间传播，也可以[[人畜共通傳染病|由其他动物传播给人]]，通常需要与感染源直接接触。<ref name="CDC2014Trans">{{Cite web|title=Transmission Nipah Virus (NiV)|url=https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/transmission/index.html|accessdate=24 May 2018|date=20 March 2014|work=CDC|language=en-us|archive-date=2018-05-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180523011637/https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/transmission/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>尼帕病毒可以基于症状和实验室检测进行诊断。<ref name="CDC2014Diag">{{Cite web|title=Diagnosis Nipah Virus (NiV)|url=https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/diagnosis/index.html|accessdate=24 May 2018|date=20 March 2014|work=CDC|language=en-us|archive-date=2019-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190615124233/https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/diagnosis/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

病患的管理仅限于[[支持性护理|支持性护理]]。<ref name="WHO2020">{{Cite web|title=Nipah Virus (NiV) Infection|url=https://www.who.int/csr/disease/nipah/en/|accessdate=14 October 2020|work=World Health Organization (WHO)|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926040108/https://www.who.int/csr/disease/nipah/en/|archivedate=26 September 2020}}</ref>{{As of|2020}}，既没有针对尼帕病毒的[[疫苗|疫苗]]，也没有针对性的治疗方法。预防措施包括避免接触蝙蝠和病猪，以及不喝生[[椰棗|椰棗]]汁。 <ref name="CDC2014Prev">{{Cite web|title=Prevention Nipah Virus (NiV)|url=https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/prevention/index.html|accessdate=24 May 2018|date=20 March 2014|work=CDC|language=en-us|archive-date=2019-06-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190615124237/https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/prevention/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>截至2018年5月，据估计已发生700例尼帕病毒人类感染病例，其中50％至75％的感染者死亡。<ref name="Chris2013">{{Cite journal|title=A treatment for and vaccine against the deadly Hendra and Nipah viruses|date=October 2013|journal=Antiviral Research|issue=1|doi=10.1016/j.antiviral.2013.06.012|volume=100|pages=8–13|pmc=4418552|pmid=23838047|display-authors=6}}</ref><ref name="SEARO2018">{{Cite web|title=Nipah virus outbreaks in the WHO South-East Asia Region|url=http://www.searo.who.int/entity/emerging_diseases/links/nipah_virus_outbreaks_sear/en/|accessdate=23 May 2018|work=South-East Asia Regional Office|publisher=WHO|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180523034319/http://www.searo.who.int/entity/emerging_diseases/links/nipah_virus_outbreaks_sear/en/|archivedate=23 May 2018}}</ref><ref name="SEAR2018May">{{Cite web|title=Morbidity and mortality due to Nipah or Nipah-like virus encephalitis in WHO South-East Asia Region, 2001-2018|url=http://www.searo.who.int/entity/emerging_diseases/links/morbidity-and-mortality-nipah-sear-2001-2018.pdf?ua=1|accessdate=2 June 2018|work=SEAR|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180613144643/http://www.searo.who.int/entity/emerging_diseases/links/morbidity-and-mortality-nipah-sear-2001-2018.pdf?ua=1|archivedate=13 June 2018|quote=112 cases since Oct 2013}}</ref> 2018年5月，该病在印度[[喀拉拉邦|喀拉拉邦]]爆发，造成17人死亡。<ref>{{Cite news|author=CNN|first=Manveena Suri|title=10 confirmed dead from Nipah virus outbreak in India|url=https://www.cnn.com/2018/05/22/health/nipah-virus-death-toll-rises-intl/index.html|accessdate=25 May 2018|work=CNN|date=22 May 2018|archive-date=2021-01-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125203637/https://www.cnn.com/2018/05/22/health/nipah-virus-death-toll-rises-intl/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Hin2018">{{Cite web|title=Nipah virus outbreak: Death toll rises to 14 in Kerala, two more cases identified|url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/nipah-virus-outbreak-death-toll-rises-to-14-in-kerala-two-more-cases-identified/story-f4QenFXeOtJnWhw7NrVawJ.html|accessdate=28 May 2018|date=27 May 2018|work=Hindustan Times|archive-date=2019-06-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190609062009/https://www.hindustantimes.com/india-news/nipah-virus-outbreak-death-toll-rises-to-14-in-kerala-two-more-cases-identified/story-f4QenFXeOtJnWhw7NrVawJ.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.frontline.in/the-nation/public-health/article24200872.ece|title=After the outbreak|work=Frontline|accessdate=2018-07-10|language=en}}</ref>

该病于1998年在[[马来西亚|马来西亚]][[1998－1999年馬來西亞立百病毒疫情|爆发]]，由[[马来亚大学医学院|马来亚大学医学院]]的研究人员首次发现。马来西亚大多数确诊患者在[[马来亚大学医学中心|马来亚大学医学中心]]接受了诊治。尼帕病毒于1999年被分离出并得到确认。<ref name="WHO2020">{{Cite web|title=Nipah Virus (NiV) Infection|url=https://www.who.int/csr/disease/nipah/en/|accessdate=14 October 2020|work=World Health Organization (WHO)|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926040108/https://www.who.int/csr/disease/nipah/en/|archivedate=26 September 2020}}</ref><ref name="CDC2018">{{Cite web|title=Nipah Virus (NiV) CDC|url=https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/index.html|accessdate=21 May 2018|work=www.cdc.gov|publisher=CDC|language=en-us|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171216043000/https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/index.html|archivedate=16 December 2017}}</ref>该病得名于马来西亚{{link-ms|双溪立百新村|Kampung Sungai Nipah}}。由于猪也可能受到感染，马来西亚当局在1999年扑杀了数百万只猪，以阻止疾病的传播，这一措施被证明是有效的。

== 症状 ==
该病于接觸后5到14天开始出现症状。<ref name="CDC2018">{{Cite web|title=Nipah Virus (NiV) CDC|url=https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/index.html|accessdate=21 May 2018|work=www.cdc.gov|publisher=CDC|language=en-us|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171216043000/https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/index.html|archivedate=16 December 2017}}</ref>最初症状表现为发烧、头痛、嗜睡，随后迷失方向和精神错乱。早期也可能出现呼吸问题。24至48小时内可能发生昏迷。潜在并发症包括致命性的[[脑炎|脑炎]]。出现呼吸困难的患者比没有[[呼吸系统疾病|呼吸系统疾病]]的患者更容易传播病毒<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Recurrent zoonotic transmission of Nipah virus into humans, Bangladesh, 2001-2007|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2815955/|date=August 2009|journal=Emerging Infectious Diseases|issue=8|doi=10.3201/eid1508.081237|volume=15|pages=1229–35|pmc=2815955|pmid=19751584|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180522034837/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pmc/articles/PMC2815955/|archivedate=22 May 2018|display-authors=6}}</ref>；超过45岁的患者同样更容易传播。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Transmission of Nipah Virus - 14 Years of Investigations in Bangladesh|date=May 2019|journal=The New England Journal of Medicine|issue=19|doi=10.1056/NEJMoa1805376|volume=380|pages=1804–1814|pmc=6547369|pmid=31067370|display-authors=6}}</ref>

== 风险性 ==
感染病毒的医院工作人员和护理人员接触的风险很高。在马来西亚和新加坡，受感染猪的密切接触者会感染尼帕病毒。在孟加拉国和印度，这种疾病与饮用未加工的[[椰棗|椰棗]]汁，食用蝙蝠吃过的水果，以及饮食蝙蝠居住的井中的水有关。<ref>{{Cite book|last=Luby|first=Stephen P.|last2=Gurley|first2=Emily S.|last3=Hossain|first3=M. Jahangir|title=Transmission of Human Infection with Nipah Virus|date=2012|publisher=National Academies Press (US)|url=https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK114486/|accessdate=21 May 2018|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180522034837/https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK114486/|archivedate=22 May 2018}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|author=Balan|first=Sarita|title=6 Nipah virus deaths in Kerala: Bat-infested house well of first victims sealed|url=https://www.thenewsminute.com/article/6-nipah-virus-deaths-kerala-bat-infested-house-well-first-victims-sealed-81650|accessdate=21 May 2018|work=The News Minute|date=21 May 2018|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180522034837/https://www.thenewsminute.com/article/6-nipah-virus-deaths-kerala-bat-infested-house-well-first-victims-sealed-81650|archivedate=22 May 2018}}</ref><gallery widths="300" heights="200">
