== 实验室诊断 ==
[[File:Nipah.jpg|缩略图]]
在该病的急性期和恢复期，可以使用逆转录酶[[聚合酶链式反应|聚合酶链反应]]（RT-PCR）从[[咽拭子|咽拭子]]、[[腦脊液|脑脊液]]、尿液和血液中进行RNA检测。<ref name="CDC2018">{{Cite web|title=Nipah Virus (NiV) CDC|url=https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/index.html|accessdate=21 May 2018|work=www.cdc.gov|publisher=CDC|language=en-us|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171216043000/https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/index.html|archivedate=16 December 2017}}</ref>

恢复后， 利用[[IgG|IgG]]和[[IgM|IgM]]抗体检测可以确认以前感染过尼帕病毒。尸检时收集[[免疫組織化學|免疫組織化學染色]]也可以确定这种疾病。<ref name="CDC2018">{{Cite web|title=Nipah Virus (NiV) CDC|url=https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/index.html|accessdate=21 May 2018|work=www.cdc.gov|publisher=CDC|language=en-us|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20171216043000/https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/index.html|archivedate=16 December 2017}}</ref>

== 治疗 ==
{{As of|2020}}，尚无尼帕病毒感染的针对性治疗方法。<ref name="Shar2019">{{Cite journal|title=Emerging trends of Nipah virus: A review.|last=Sharma|first=V|last2=Kaushik|first2=S|date=January 2019|journal=Reviews in Medical Virology|issue=1|doi=10.1002/rmv.2010|volume=29|pages=e2010|pmid=30251294|last3=Kumar|first3=R|last4=Yadav|first4=JP|last5=Kaushik|first5=S|subscription=free}}</ref>治疗主要采用[[支持性护理|支持性护理]]。<ref name="CDC2014Tx">{{Cite web|title=Nipah Virus (NiV) - Treatment|url=https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/treatment/index.html|date=20 March 2014|work=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC)|access-date=2021-02-02|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202062545/https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/treatment/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Shar20193">{{cite journal|title=Emerging trends of Nipah virus: A review.|first1=V|last2=Kaushik|first2=S|date=January 2019|journal=Reviews in Medical Virology|issue=1|doi=10.1002/rmv.2010|volume=29|pages=e2010|pmid=30251294|last3=Kumar|first3=R|last4=Yadav|first4=JP|last5=Kaushik|first5=S|last1=Sharma|doi-access=free}}</ref>建议采用标准感染控制措施和适当的屏障护理技术，以避免人与人之间的传播。<ref name="CDC2014Tx4">{{cite web|title=Nipah Virus (NiV) - Treatment|url=https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/treatment/index.html|date=20 March 2014|website=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC)|access-date=2021-02-02|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202062545/https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/treatment/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>所有疑似感染尼帕病毒者都应进行隔离。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Nipah yet to be confirmed, 86 under observation: Shailaja|url=https://english.manoramaonline.com/news/kerala/2019/06/03/nipah-case-kochi-thodupuzha-kk-shilaja.html|accessdate=2019-06-04|work=OnManorama|language=en|archive-date=2019-07-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190708180108/https://english.manoramaonline.com/news/kerala/2019/06/03/nipah-case-kochi-thodupuzha-kk-shilaja.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>虽然有初步证据支持[[利巴韦林|利巴韦林]]的使用，但该药物尚未就该病患者进行研究。<ref name="CDC2014Tx3">{{cite web|title=Nipah Virus (NiV) - Treatment|url=https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/treatment/index.html|date=20 March 2014|website=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC)|access-date=2021-02-02|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202062545/https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/treatment/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>有动物模型研究表明特异性抗体具有潜在益处。<ref name="CDC2014Tx2">{{cite web|title=Nipah Virus (NiV) - Treatment|url=https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/treatment/index.html|date=20 March 2014|website=Centers for Disease Control and Prevention (CDC)|access-date=2021-02-02|archive-date=2021-02-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210202062545/https://www.cdc.gov/vhf/nipah/treatment/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>[[阿昔洛韦|阿昔洛韦]]、[[法匹拉韦|法匹拉韦]]<ref name="Shar20192">{{cite journal|title=Emerging trends of Nipah virus: A review.|first1=V|last2=Kaushik|first2=S|date=January 2019|journal=Reviews in Medical Virology|issue=1|doi=10.1002/rmv.2010|volume=29|pages=e2010|pmid=30251294|last3=Kumar|first3=R|last4=Yadav|first4=JP|last5=Kaushik|first5=S|last1=Sharma|doi-access=free}}</ref>和[[瑞德西韦|瑞德西韦]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Remdesivir (GS-5734) protects African green monkeys from Nipah virus challenge|last=Lo|first=Michael K.|last2=Feldmann|first2=Friederike|date=2019-05-29|journal=Science Translational Medicine|issue=494|doi=10.1126/scitranslmed.aau9242|volume=11|pages=eaau9242|language=en|issn=1946-6234|pmc=6732787|pmid=31142680|last3=Gary|first3=Joy M.|last4=Jordan|first4=Robert|last5=Bannister|first5=Roy|last6=Cronin|first6=Jacqueline|last7=Patel|first7=Nishi R.|last8=Klena|first8=John D.|last9=Nichol|first9=Stuart T.}}</ref>已被评估为潜在抗尼帕病毒药物。

== 爆发 ==
[[File:Hendra-distribution-map.jpg|左]]
马来西亚、新加坡、孟加拉国和印度都报告过尼帕病毒的爆发。孟加拉国录得尼帕病毒的最高死亡率， 爆发时间通常在冬天。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Nipah virus-associated encephalitis outbreak, Siliguri, India|date=February 2006|journal=Emerging Infectious Diseases|issue=2|doi=10.3201/eid1202.051247|volume=12|pages=235–40|pmc=3373078|pmid=16494748|display-authors=6}}</ref>尼帕病毒最早于1998年在马来西亚半岛的猪和养猪户中发现。至1999年年中，马来西亚已报告265例人类脑炎病例，其中105例死亡；新加坡报告11例脑炎或呼吸系统疾病病例，其中1例死亡。<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Hendra and Nipah viruses: different and dangerous|url=https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/e2fa28014678481b60ce11cdc3c1fe4709533c32|date=January 2006|journal=Nature Reviews. Microbiology|issue=1|doi=10.1038/nrmicro1323|volume=4|pages=23–35|pmc=7097447|pmid=16357858|access-date=2021-02-02|archive-date=2021-08-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210828185433/https://www.semanticscholar.org/paper/Hendra-and-Nipah-viruses%3A-different-and-dangerous-Eaton-Broder/e2fa28014678481b60ce11cdc3c1fe4709533c32|dead-url=no}}</ref>2001年，孟加拉国[[梅黑尔布尔县|梅黑尔布尔县]]<ref name="chadha">{{Cite journal|title=Nipah virus-associated encephalitis outbreak, Siliguri, India|date=February 2006|journal=Emerging Infectious Diseases|issue=2|doi=10.3201/eid1202.051247|volume=12|pages=235–40|pmc=3373078|pmid=16494748|display-authors=6}}</ref><ref name="hsu">{{Cite journal|title=Nipah virus encephalitis reemergence, Bangladesh|date=December 2004|journal=Emerging Infectious Diseases|issue=12|doi=10.3201/eid1012.040701|volume=10|pages=2082–7|pmc=3323384|pmid=15663842|display-authors=6}}</ref>和印度[[西里古里|西里古里]]报告尼帕病毒。<ref name="chadha" />2003、2004和2005年，孟加拉国[[瑙冈县|瑙冈县]]、[[马尼格甘杰县|马尼格甘杰县]]、[[拉杰巴里县|拉杰巴里县]]、[[福里德布尔县|福里德布尔县]]和[[坦盖尔县|坦盖尔县]]再次爆发尼帕病毒。<ref name="hsu" />随后几年，孟加拉国又有疫情爆发。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Basic preventive measures can reduce Nipah virus attack|url=https://www.thedailystar.net/news-detail-26658|author=<!--not stated-->|date=8 March 2008|work=The Daily Star (Bangladesh)|access-date=2021-02-02|archive-date=2020-10-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201015022317/https://www.thedailystar.net/news-detail-26658|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="SEARO20182">{{Cite web|title=Nipah virus outbreaks in the WHO South-East Asia Region|url=http://www.searo.who.int/entity/emerging_diseases/links/nipah_virus_outbreaks_sear/en/|accessdate=23 May 2018|work=South-East Asia Regional Office|publisher=WHO|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20180523034319/http://www.searo.who.int/entity/emerging_diseases/links/nipah_virus_outbreaks_sear/en/|archivedate=23 May 2018}}</ref>

* [[1998－1999年馬來西亞立百病毒疫情|1998年9月至1999年5月]]：[[马来西亚|马来西亚]][[霹靂州|霹雳州]]、[[森美兰|森美兰州]]和[[雪蘭莪|雪兰莪州]]，三个州共报告了265例由该病毒引起的急性[[脑炎|脑炎，]]其中105例死亡。<ref name="lessons from Nipah outbreak">{{Cite journal|title=Lessons from the Nipah virus outbreak in Malaysia|url=http://www.mjpath.org.my/2007.2/02Nipah_Virus_lessons.pdf|date=2007|journal=The Malaysian Journal of Pathology|publisher=Department of Pathology, University of Malaya and National Public Health Laboratory of the Ministry of Health, Malaysia|volume=29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190830060915/http://www.mjpath.org.my/2007.2/02Nipah_Virus_lessons.pdf|archivedate=30 August 2019|number=2}}</ref>[[马来西亚卫生部|马来西亚卫生部]]起初以为[[流行性乙型脑炎|日本脑炎]]是感染原因，这一观点阻碍了防止尼帕病毒传播的有效措施的部署。<ref name="lessons from Nipah outbreak2">{{Cite journal|title=Lessons from the Nipah virus outbreak in Malaysia|url=http://www.mjpath.org.my/2007.2/02Nipah_Virus_lessons.pdf|date=2007|journal=The Malaysian Journal of Pathology|publisher=Department of Pathology, University of Malaya and National Public Health Laboratory of the Ministry of Health, Malaysia|volume=29|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20190830060915/http://www.mjpath.org.my/2007.2/02Nipah_Virus_lessons.pdf|archivedate=30 August 2019|number=2}}</ref>
